indices.Message:
Slam your fist into the ground and
surround yourself with pillars of alchemical metal. When 
performed from high altitudes, the power of the attack rises.
Can be activated even while in the air.
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Increases amount of stakes planted upon contact.
LV.6: Increases the times the pillars raise (1→2)</COL>

Place your palm on the ground and upon
raising it, create waves of alchemical substances that spike
up along the ground.
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Increases amount of stakes planted upon contact. 
LV.6: Increases number of waves (3→5) and adds the ability 
to juggle enemies.</COL>

Create an elemental orb that bestows
one of the three main attributes of fire, ice, or lightning,
from the ground and place it in the air.
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Increases duration of the skill.
LV.6: Unlocks the final two elements, Holy and Darkness.</COL>

Place an alchemical trampoline on the ground
that launches those who jump on it to high altitudes.
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Increases duration of the skill.
LV.6: Allows placement in the air. When placed mid-air,
you can be launched horizontally.</COL>

Create a ball of wind-wrapped alchemical substances.
Wind pressure is generated when striking the ball after placement.
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Increases duration of the skill.
LV.6: Increases range of wind pressure generated when struck.</COL>

Drive alchemical piles into enemies, and quickly draw
their aggression. If a pile is struck, the amount of stakes on it will increase.
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Increases duration of the skill.
LV.6: Increases chase range of skill, and amount of alchemical
stakes gained upon striking the pile.</COL>

Generate a trap from an alchemical substance.
When enemies approach the trap, pillars spike out from it and 
penetrate them.
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Increases number of trap activations.
LV.6: Increases the number of pillar spikes (1→3)</COL>

Coat yourself in gold and deflect enemy attacks.
Enemies that attack will build up the "Gilded" status abnormality.
Can be activated even while in the air.
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Increases rate of Gilding build-up.
LV.6: Can activate the skill at anytime except when grabbed.</COL>

Bring forth a giant metal arm that strikes the 
enemy directly and can adhere to them if it hits an alchemical stake.
Upon doing so, it unleashes alchemical substances and causes a
giant explosion.
Can be activated while climbing an enemy.
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Increases damage of skill.
LV.6: Increases number of hits and the surrounding
enemies are affected by the explosion.</COL>

Jump up and form a trap from an
alchemical substance in the air. When deployed,
quickly launch backwards.
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Increases number of trap activations.
LV.6: Allows activation while mid-air.</COL>
